                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18001029-39-defend326 t18001029-39-punish223"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>

               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
